LN7LsrafWBFpzw">Ký hữu - 寄友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-S%C4%A9/author-WQkvak0bO6BDMarTsB2kng">Ngô Thì Sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%AD-Ho%C3%A0/Ng%C6%B0-ca-t%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-W0IGstZn6UgYVwNXwDotWw">Ngư ca tử kỳ 3 - 漁歌子其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%AD-Ho%C3%A0/author-K-KPc0BUQdzcRKS-f2QraA">Trương Chí Hoà</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/T%C3%BAc-H%E1%BA%ADu-L%E1%BB%99c-d%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-byzvzbeaWBZT9yvqA8_Cyw">Túc Hậu Lộc dạ vũ hữu cảm - 宿厚祿夜雨有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-ioE9gUDRRK0CF1f-0I-Dgw">Châu Hải Đường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%C3%B9ng-thanh/poem-JEwWLUc9JhHbaxGqyeGeEg">Tùng thanh - 松聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/T%E1%BB%B1-k%C3%ADch-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh/poem-6_e1mRhX4VCaxYlmvQaZlw">Tự kích ngẫu thành - 自激偶成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/author-Pf4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br></div>	</div>
